summary: Nice times underwater making sure there ain't no Toxapex still lingering ----------------------------------- Neat-o Trivia...
caption:
Nice times underwater making sure there ain’t no Toxapex still lingering

———————————–

Neat-o Trivia
-Baloo keeps a Lanturn for underwater exploring. She likes swimming but doesn’t like being blind in a place that hasn’t been fully explored. The Lanturn is super overweight because Baloo is really bad at saying no to begging faces
-She used to keep a Drampa for surfing and diving but he prefers hanging out on land and eating flowers. Not for food or anything but just cause they’re there
-Ty still has a surfing Dhelmise and just for fun uses Scylla for diving. Because she’s so big she can dive and keep going without having to worry about how cold it is or the pressure
-This doesn’t do much for Ty or Baloo since their oxygen supplier will actually start to drop pretty fast if they go down too far and Scylla is trained to recognize this and back up

Loudred shouts while stamping its feet. After it finishes shouting, this Pokemon becomes incapable of hearing anything for a while. This is considered to be a weak point.
